    "The generator improves with discriminator feedback.",
    "The generator will cease training if the discriminator is too strong.",
    "Because it can detect false images [58].",
    "The parameters of neural networks are determined utilizing back-propagation methods.",
    "These techniques were using a chain rule that moves layer by layer to estimate the gain of the loss function with respect to the network parameters."
